            "Dense top-5 sources:\n",
            "  products/WK-SW-001_wongkhojon_watch_s3_ultra.md\n",
            "  products/WK-SW-003_wongkhojon_watch_s3.md\n",
            "  products/WK-SW-002_wongkhojon_watch_s3_pro.md\n",
